          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1619713667833-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the wedges are in the oven, peel and finely slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into rings</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallots</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Set aside to pickle – these are your <strong>pickled shallots</strong></p>",
