      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>beef mince</strong> to a bowl with generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>and mix thoroughly with clean hands for 1 min until fully combined (this helps them to hold their shape whilst cooking)</p><p>Divide the mince into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span>, shape them into patties and refrigerate until later</p>",
