    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>beef patties </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on one side, or until browned</p><p>Once browned, flip the patties and top with the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Cover loosely with a lid (or some<strong> tin foil</strong>!) and cook for 2-3 min further or until the cheese has melted and the patties are cooked through</p>",
