    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>pickled shallots</strong> (discard the pickling liquid), then spread each <strong>brioche base</strong> with <strong>mayo </strong>and each <strong>brioche lid</strong> with<strong> chilli jam</strong></p><p>To assemble, top the <strong>brioche base</strong> with the <strong>pickled shallots</strong>, some<strong> lettuce leaves</strong>, a <strong>cheesy patty</strong>, some <strong>peanut butter</strong> and a <strong>brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>smoky wedges</strong> to the side and enjoy!</p>",
